title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2010-12 Camaro LED Tail Lights
description: This video provides specific directions for how to install Spyder Auto's LED tail lights in 2009-11 5th Generation Camaro models. Several styles of LED tail lights are available, however the method of installation is the same.
